      <description>&lt;p&gt;Welcome to Wenjun Zhang&#39;s homepage! I am a graduate student at the University of Chicago Pritzker School of Molecular Engineering (PME). My research interests include atomic, molecular and optical (AMO) physics and quantum simulation. Advised by Prof. Hannes Bernien, I&#39;m excited to investigate the physics of quantum many-body systems with long-range interactions by using Rydberg atom arrays.&lt;/p&gt;
